title: 6 Crime ePUBs (gnv64)
description:
A collection of six ePUBs on crime with an additional PDF:

1. Inherit the Dead: A Novel by Lee Child, C. J. Box, Charlaine Harris and John Connolly (Oct 8, 2013)
   
2. Practically Perfect: Killers Who Got Away with Murder ... for a While by Dale Brawn (Jul 30, 2013) 
   
3. Rampage: Canadian Mass Murder and Spree Killing by Lee Mellor (Apr 2, 2013) 
   
4. The Good Nurse: A True Story of Medicine, Madness, and Murder by Charles Graeber (Apr 15, 2013) 
   
5. The Killer Book of Cold Cases: Incredible Stories, Facts, and Trivia from the Most Baffling True Crime Cases of All Time by Tom Philbin (Feb 1, 2012)
   
6. The law killers: True Crime from Dundee by McGregor, Alexander (Sep 4, 2013) 
   

7. Life without Parole - America's New Death Penalty? by Jr. Charles J. Ogletree and Austin Sarat (Jun 4, 2012)
